  "aboutHeading": "About Inspired Fitness",
  "aboutBody": [
    "Inspired Fitness Training Center has been Sebastopol's neighborhood fitness home since 2006. It is owned by Jennifer Fujii, a three-time United States gold medalist in aerobic gymnastics, and her husband John, who built it into the kind of gym members call the Cheers of gyms, where the team knows your name and you feel right at home.",
    "Beyond the classes and one-on-one training, the center is home to Inspired Juice, serving cold-pressed juices, smoothies, avocado toast, and grab-and-go, so a workout and a fresh juice live under one roof."
  ],
